<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">January 2021 was a really bad time for movie t=
heaters, which were battered by Covid closures and the film industry=E2=80=
=99s embrace of streaming. But it was a really good time for AMC Entertainm=
ent Holdings Inc., a big movie-theater company, because it was the height o=
f the meme-stock craze and AMC was a meme stock. Its revenue was low but it=
s stock was high. AMC seized the moment by selling stock and converting deb=
t into equity at its meme-inflated stock price. <a href=3D"https://link.mai=
l.bloombergbusiness.com/click/28989079.279539/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnL=
mNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMDEtMjgva25vd2luZy13aGVuLXRvLXNlbGwtZ2Ft=
