 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-=
color: #ccc;">kicked off last week</a>, so if you are a top investment bank=
ing analyst you probably have your 2024 private equity job lined up by this=
 point. Which means that you missed out on <a href=3D"https://link.mail.blo=
ombergbusiness.com/click/28989079.279539/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLmNvbS9hcnRpY2=
xlcy9raW0ta2FyZGFzaGlhbnMtbGF0ZXN0LWJ1c2luZXNzLXZlbnR1cmUtcHJpdmF0ZS1lcXVpd=
